when I was 8.

02:40.667 --> 02:44.834
"Absolutely no parties
involving pajamas, music,

02:44.834 --> 02:47.868
"or shaving Daddy's head
while he sleeps,

02:47.868 --> 02:49.334
"until you're 16.

02:49.334 --> 02:52.167
Signed, your father,
God help me, Al Bundy."

02:52.167 --> 02:58.701
