I thought I'd be dead by now.

02:58.701 --> 03:00.534
Well, the joke's
on you, Dad.

03:00.534 --> 03:03.901
No. Actually,
the joke's on me.

03:03.901 --> 03:05.868
But not very often.

03:10.934 --> 03:12.534
Hey, Kel.

03:12.534 --> 03:15.000
Word through the peephole
in the girls' shower room

03:15.000 --> 03:17.100
