is squirting me.

03:28.033 --> 03:31.100
Mom, please,
it's girls only.

03:31.100 --> 03:32.100
Can't you
send him somewhere,

03:32.100 --> 03:33.901
like Steve and Marcy's,

03:33.901 --> 03:36.801
