it's a normal Saturday night.

03:51.334 --> 03:53.067
Turn the lights down low,

03:53.067 --> 03:54.801
put on some soft music,

03:54.801 --> 03:56.901
and dial 1-800-NO-DATE.

03:59.367 --> 04:00.534
No, Kel.

04:00.534 --> 04:02.033
