outside your window.

04:07.567 --> 04:09.033
Eat toe rot.

04:09.033 --> 04:10.701
Lick road kill.

04:10.701 --> 04:12.968
You know, I'm getting hungry.

04:15.501 --> 04:16.701
Thanks, Mom.

04:16.701 --> 04:19.334
Oh, by the way, on party night,

04:19.334 --> 04:21.601
I want you two in your room
by 7:00,

04:21.601 --> 04:23.934
