16:23.167 --> 16:24.467
It would have been all over

16:24.467 --> 16:25.834
except promises

16:25.834 --> 16:27.467
of a better performance
next time.

16:27.467 --> 16:30.000
Don't pay any
attention to her.

16:30.000 --> 16:31.567
I'm glad
you kids are here.

16:31.567 --> 16:34.434
Stay as long
as you want.

16:34.434 --> 16:35.734
Thanks, Al.

16:35.734 --> 16:36.834
We're suing you,
you know.

16:36.834 --> 16:38.934
Fine.

16:38.934 --> 16:40.868
Take it all.
I've had too much for too long.

16:43.434 --> 16:44.667
Let's just all go to sleep

16:44.667 --> 16:47.868
so this day of a thousand deaths
can end.

16:51.100 --> 16:54.734
[CONTENTED SIGH]
[CONTENTED SIGH]

16:54.734 --> 16:58.868
[MUSIC BLARES]

16:58.868 --> 17:00.000
This is horrible.

17:00.000 --> 17:01.801
I just can't
take it anymore.

17:01.801 --> 17:02.801
Don't worry, Marcy.

17:02.801 --> 17:04.000
We'll get our house
back tomorrow.

17:04.000 --> 17:05.000
It's not that.

17:05.000 --> 17:06.867
I smell Al's feet.

17:14.434 --> 17:16.099
Can you
believe Charlene?

17:16.099 --> 17:17.367
What a loser.

17:17.367 --> 17:18.733
God, I hate her.

17:18.733 --> 17:20.032
She's so phony.

17:20.032 --> 17:22.934
And a boring slob.

17:22.934 --> 17:24.733
She couldn't turn a boy on
with a switch.

17:24.733 --> 17:25.733
I know.

17:25.733 --> 17:28.200
She's so gross.

17:28.200 --> 17:29.367
Oh, hi, Charlene.

17:29.367 --> 17:30.834
You look great.

17:30.834 --> 17:32.167
You know, we were just saying

17:32.167 --> 17:34.567
that you must have to
beat the boys off with a stick.

17:34.567 --> 17:36.434
My turn.

17:40.667 --> 17:41.968
God, I hate her.

17:41.968 --> 17:44.000
She is so annoying.

17:44.000 --> 17:45.167
[ALL TALKING]

17:59.701 --> 18:02.534
Good evening, ladies.

18:04.567 --> 18:07.200
Just a little reminder.

18:07.200 --> 18:09.067
When you get tired
of the endless drone

18:09.067 --> 18:10.534
of girlish chatter,

18:10.534 --> 18:12.601
step up to pleasure.

18:12.601 --> 18:14.834
Step up to "Club Bud."

18:19.601 --> 18:23.367
Get out of here,
you little she-male.

18:23.367 --> 18:24.868
No, that's okay, let him stay.

18:24.868 --> 18:26.634
I think he's cute.

18:26.634 --> 18:28.834
You and the rest of the world,
babe.

18:30.567 --> 18:33.267
Oh, Bud,
you drive me crazy.

18:33.267 --> 18:35.667
Let me give you
something special.

18:35.667 --> 18:37.400
Close your eyes.

18:42.133 --> 18:43.868
Pucker up, baby.

18:48.868 --> 18:51.868
Come on, baby.
Give me all you got.

18:59.000 --> 19:01.767
Ha, ha. Very funny.

19:01.767 --> 19:03.033
Very funny.

19:03.033 --> 19:07.601
It's another fine example
of bimbo wit.

19:07.601 --> 19:09.767
I'm done. Finished.
I'm going upstairs.

19:09.767 --> 19:10.834
Oh, Bud, before you go,

19:10.834 --> 19:13.467
can you say, "I'm drinking milk,

19:13.467 --> 19:16.067
and one day,
I'm gonna be big and strong"?

19:18.834 --> 19:21.501
Tee-hee, Kel.

19:21.501 --> 19:24.501
Oh, by the way, I almost forgot.

19:24.501 --> 19:27.400
There were a few messages
for you.

19:27.400 --> 19:28.667
Let me see.

19:28.667 --> 19:30.367
Oh. Dan Peterson called.

19:30.367 --> 19:31.601
He said tomorrow night

19:31.601 --> 19:34.033
behind the 7-Eleven
would be fine.

19:34.033 --> 19:36.234
Uh, Bud,
I don't think

19:36.234 --> 19:37.734
that anybody
wants to hear this.

19:37.734 --> 19:39.968
Dan Peterson.
That's my boyfriend.

19:39.968 --> 19:41.334
Oh, is he?

19:43.367 --> 19:46.067
Gee, Kelly thinks he's hers.

19:46.067 --> 19:47.200
Oh, well.

19:47.200 --> 19:48.200
Let's see.

19:48.200 --> 19:50.601
Um, Greg Barnett called too.

19:50.601 --> 19:52.200
You have a date with him
Tuesday.

19:52.200 --> 19:55.567
Oh, "And wear something tight."

19:55.567 --> 19:56.934
Wait a minute.

19:56.934 --> 19:58.734
I'm dating Greg.

19:58.734 --> 20:00.067
Uh-oh.

20:00.067 --> 20:01.133
Well.

20:01.133 --> 20:02.767
Let's see.

20:02.767 --> 20:04.601
Whose boyfriend
is Bobby Brocatto?

20:04.601 --> 20:05.868
Mine.
Mine.

20:09.601 --> 20:12.334
Well. You guys
have a lot to talk about.

20:12.334 --> 20:13.701
Good night.

20:15.133 --> 20:17.767
You're seeing
my Greg?

20:17.767 --> 20:18.968
And Dan?

20:18.968 --> 20:21.868
Well, I wasn't
going to keep them.

20:21.868 --> 20:22.968
Sow.

20:22.968 --> 20:23.968
Trollop.

20:23.968 --> 20:24.968
Tramp.

20:24.968 --> 20:25.968
Slut.

20:25.968 --> 20:26.834
Bundy.

20:30.701 --> 20:32.033
What do you think
you're doing?

20:32.033 --> 20:34.434
It's your fault!

20:34.434 --> 20:37.300
[ALL SHOUTING]

20:43.701 --> 20:46.267
Yum, yum, give me some.

20:56.367 --> 21:02.501
How can he get that smell
with only 10 toes?

21:02.501 --> 21:04.000
Go to sleep, Marcy.

21:04.000 --> 21:05.634
I can't. I'm too upset.

21:05.634 --> 21:08.400
I miss our little house.

21:08.400 --> 21:09.634
I know,

21:09.634 --> 21:12.467
but we'll get it back,
angel cups.

21:12.467 --> 21:13.667
You haven't called
me angel cups

21:13.667 --> 21:17.200
in a long time,
sugar tush.

21:19.934 --> 21:21.601
Remember what I said

21:21.601 --> 21:24.467
when we didn't think
we could afford a house?

21:24.467 --> 21:26.801
We need no home.

21:26.801 --> 21:29.367
Our love is shelter enough
against any storm.

21:35.701 --> 21:39.434
Man, thy name is Steve.

21:39.434 --> 21:41.300
And, love,
thy name is Marcy.

21:44.200 --> 21:47.100
The warmth of your arms
is my hearth.

21:47.100 --> 21:50.734
And your strong arms
are my support beams.

21:50.734 --> 21:52.868
And your lips
are my doorways to heaven.

21:52.868 --> 21:56.334
And your blue eyes are
the windows to my world.

21:56.334 --> 21:57.200
And your hair--

22:04.667 --> 22:06.234
Where are
you guys going?

22:06.234 --> 22:10.000
We're going to sleep
in the hole, Bud.

22:10.000 --> 22:11.334
Good night, kids.

22:11.334 --> 22:12.334
Oh, Kelly.

22:12.334 --> 22:14.267
Huh?

22:14.267 --> 22:16.033
Honey, remember,
no boys.

22:16.033 --> 22:17.901
Okay, Mom.

22:17.901 --> 22:18.868
Good girl.

22:20.701 --> 22:22.868
Oh, Al, it's raining.

22:22.868 --> 22:24.801
Good. I'll sleep
with my mouth open.

22:24.801 --> 22:26.868
Maybe I'll drown.

